meanings: Noun 美속어 알았음, 오케이(cf. TEN ROGER).
[화학] 104번 원소(rutherfordium) ((12번째의 초(超)우라늄 원소, 인공 방사성 원소))

Chemical Formula C13H13N3O3. A chemical structure of a molecule includes the arrangement of atoms and the chemical bonds that hold the atoms together. The 10B-104 molecule contains of 13 Hydrogen atom(s), 13 Carbon atom(s), 3 Nitrogen atom(s) and 3 Oxygen atom(s) – a total of 32 atom(s).
